- Added cfn-signal helper script to signal CloudFormation, if Bootstrapping fails.
- Resolved exception handling issues while installing OpenShift Container Platform. 
- Added new methods to handle IBM Cloud Pak for Security installation and for getting CP4S FQDN.
- Added fail-safe to code during IBM Cloud Pak for Security installation so that the script stops execution and exit, if any of the installation stage ran into a problem and returns non zero exit status.
- Updated taskcat file and removed pyca folder in scripts as it's no longer needed.
